member.name: T:Impinj.OctaneSdk.TagQtSetOp
member.summary: Used to set Monza QT tag chip features. The tag operation can be added to the reader with the or method, or by inclusion in the list of tag operations of a object. Through QT technology, a tag owner/user can maintain two data profiles (one public, one private), allowing confidentiality of business-sensitive data while assuring consumers of privacy. The tag owner stores confidential data in the private data profile, which is protected by a password-controlled command and may only be accessed at very short read distances.
